(wind blows in the background)

00:16:58.667 --> 00:17:01.367 position:33% line:89% align:start
(door creaks)

00:17:05.367 --> 00:17:07.734 position:30% line:89% align:start
(gasps loudly)

00:17:09.267 --> 00:17:11.567 position:33% line:89% align:start
(jazzy music)

00:17:22.667 --> 00:17:28.200 position:10% line:83% align:start
- Noddle-Pete told me this is
where they kept prisoners in

00:17:28.234 --> 00:17:31.200 position:21% line:83% align:start
the olden days, down
here in the dark.

00:17:34.234 --> 00:17:36.400 position:19% line:89% align:start
Never seeing daylight.

00:17:36.434 --> 00:17:38.534 position:13% line:89% align:start
Locked up until they died.

00:17:41.667 --> 00:17:43.634 position:38% line:89% align:start
(shivers)

00:17:45.701 --> 00:17:48.367 position:33% line:89% align:start
(jazzy music)

00:18:09.200 --> 00:18:12.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
- These dungeons are
under Hell's Gap.

00:18:12.200 --> 00:18:14.734 position:24% line:83% align:start
On the stormy night
when you were born,

00:18:14.767 --> 00:18:17.501 position:30% line:83% align:start
the whole place
was split in two,

00:18:17.534 --> 00:18:22.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
with rocks and rubble
covering this whole area.

00:18:22.501 --> 00:18:26.400 position:27% line:83% align:start
And so the entire
passageway was cut in half.

00:18:26.434 --> 00:18:30.267 position:24% line:83% align:start
And this is as far
as you can safely go.

00:18:30.300 --> 00:18:32.534 position:7% line:89% align:start
- As far as you can safely go.

00:18:33.834 --> 00:18:36.534 position:33% line:89% align:start
(jazzy music)

00:18:40.467 --> 00:18:44.634 position:13% line:83% align:start
But on the other side, the
passage way, it must carry on.

00:18:47.267 --> 00:18:49.567 position:10% line:89% align:start
I will get to the other side.

00:18:51.767 --> 00:18:54.601 position:27% line:83% align:start
All this rock and
rubble can't stop me.

00:18:54.634 --> 00:18:57.567 position:27% line:83% align:start
Birk's there, and
I will get to him.

00:19:03.501 --> 00:19:06.234 position:27% line:89% align:start
(loud shoveling)

00:19:10.634 --> 00:19:11.701 position:38% line:89% align:start
- Anyone?

00:19:11.734 --> 00:19:14.067 position:13% line:89% align:start
Anyone seen Ronja recently?

00:19:14.100 --> 00:19:17.601 position:24% line:83% align:start
I wonder what she's
been doing with herself.

00:19:17.634 --> 00:19:21.667 position:10% line:83% align:start
- That child is impulsive and
comes and goes as she likes.

00:19:21.701 --> 00:19:26.000 position:10% line:83% align:start
- I bet she's shoveling snow
with the rest (chuckles).

00:19:27.501 --> 00:19:28.534 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Hmm.

00:19:32.601 --> 00:19:35.567 position:21% line:89% align:start
(inspirational music)

00:19:37.734 --> 00:19:40.200 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:19:47.634 --> 00:19:50.567 position:27% line:89% align:start
(whimsical horn)

00:19:54.434 --> 00:19:56.667 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:20:07.534 --> 00:20:10.133 position:30% line:89% align:start
(pants softly)

00:20:11.601 --> 00:20:14.367 position:30% line:89% align:start
(light flutes)

00:20:22.501 --> 00:20:26.334 position:19% line:83% align:start
- If I see Birk again,
we'll be able to talk.

00:20:27.801 --> 00:20:34.334 position:16% line:83% align:start
And then I will find out
if he really is my brother

00:20:34.367 --> 00:20:37.400 position:5% line:89% align:start
as he promised in the snowstorm,

00:20:37.434 --> 00:20:41.200 position:10% line:89% align:start
when he called me his sister.

00:20:43.400 --> 00:20:46.000 position:30% line:89% align:start
(jovial music)

00:20:49.334 --> 00:20:52.567 position:16% line:89% align:start
(breathing and grunting)

00:20:54.367 --> 00:20:58.200 position:10% line:89% align:start
(crowd laughing and chatting)

00:20:59.501 --> 00:21:02.200 position:30% line:89% align:start
(beating drums)

00:21:03.334 --> 00:21:07.167 position:10% line:89% align:start
(crowd laughing and shouting)

00:21:08.567 --> 00:21:10.400 position:30% line:89% align:start
- From now on,

00:21:10.434 --> 00:21:12.400 position:21% line:89% align:start
so long as I'm alive,

00:21:12.434 --> 00:21:18.701 position:19% line:83% align:start
never again am I going
to move any stones,

00:21:18.734 --> 00:21:21.467 position:33% line:89% align:start
big or small.

00:21:22.501 --> 00:21:25.434 position:24% line:89% align:start
(light orchestral)

00:21:29.501 --> 00:21:32.367 position:27% line:89% align:start
(stones rustling)

00:21:32.400 --> 00:21:35.267 position:27% line:89% align:start
(light grunting)

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:46.767 position:27% line:89% align:start
(light grunting)

00:21:48.667 --> 00:21:51.133 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:21:57.434 --> 00:21:58.434 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:22:00.334 --> 00:22:03.367 position:10% line:89% align:start
Come on, why won't you move!

00:22:05.167 --> 00:22:08.434 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh Birk, it seemed
like such a good idea!

00:22:08.467 --> 00:22:11.334 position:24% line:89% align:start
(light orchestral)

00:22:15.434 --> 00:22:18.100 position:30% line:89% align:start
(rocks pouring)

00:22:23.501 --> 00:22:26.400 position:27% line:83% align:start
- [Narrator] Day
after day, bit by bit,

00:22:26.434 --> 00:22:29.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
Ronja continued to
haul the rocks away.

00:22:33.400 --> 00:22:34.334 position:35% line:89% align:start
And then...

00:22:41.067 --> 00:22:43.601 position:27% line:89% align:start
(soft wind blow)

00:22:48.300 --> 00:22:51.234 position:24% line:89% align:start
(distant rustling)

00:22:53.434 --> 00:22:55.667 position:24% line:89% align:start
(distant footsteps)

00:22:57.267 --> 00:23:02.667 position:13% line:83% align:start
Finally a breakthrough, but
Ronja knew that she was on

00:23:02.701 --> 00:23:04.367 position:27% line:89% align:start
dangerous ground.

00:23:08.200 --> 00:23:11.601 position:13% line:83% align:start
All the same, she couldn't
stop herself from wanting

00:23:11.634 --> 00:23:13.300 position:30% line:89% align:start
to reach Birk.

00:23:13.334 --> 00:23:18.267 position:21% line:83% align:start
She longed to see the
boy she called Brother.

00:23:18.300 --> 00:23:20.300 position:33% line:89% align:start
(banjo music)

00:23:20.334 --> 00:23:24.367 position:24% line:83% align:start
Next time on Ronja,
the Robber's Daughter.

00:23:24.400 --> 00:23:27.634 position:33% line:89% align:start
(banjo music)

00:23:27.667 --> 00:23:29.701 position:13% line:89% align:start
"The Whistler Underground".

00:23:31.467 --> 00:23:32.634 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't miss it.

